Comment: I'm black here and open with Fisher/Reti.  It sets up an early queenside attack, a blunder by white, and an early 3 point advantage.  Due to sheer stupidity, I lose a big advantage and am forced to accept a stalemate in the end.  Lesson learned, don't get overly confident.
